ca.mcgill.ecse211.project

Class main

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.mcgill.ecse211.project.main

  • public class main
extends java.lang.Object
    The goal of this software is to make a robot play a capture the flag game against another robot. The robot needs to be able to localize, travel to certain points in a (12X12) grid, cross a zipline and find the opponent's flag. Here are the tasks it needs to perform in under 5 minutes:
    1. Get the parameters from the server
    2. Transit to the opponent's zone using the zipline or the shallow water
    3. Find the opponent's flag
    4. Transit the its own zone using the other method
    5. Go back to its starting position
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Vincent d'Orsonnens, Chen He
